#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.45"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.45:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Uposathavagga"
msgstr "5. Sabbath"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 45. Bojjhasutta → bojjhaṅguposathasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Bojjhasutta"
msgstr "45. With Bojjhā on the Sabbath"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "an8.45:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bojjhā upāsikā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho bojjhaṃ "
"upāsikaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the laywoman Bojjhā went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one "
"side. The Buddha said to her:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.260"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgato, bojjhe, uposatho upavuttho mahapphalo hoti mahānisaṃso "
"mahājutiko mahāvipphāro."
msgstr ""
"“Bojjhā, the observance of the sabbath with its eight factors is very "
"fruitful and beneficial and splendid and bountiful."

msgctxt "an8.45:2.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ upavuttho ca, bojjhe, aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgato uposatho mahapphalo hoti "
"mahānisaṃso mahājutiko mahāvipphāro?"
msgstr "And how should it be observed?"

msgctxt "an8.45:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bojjhe, ariyasāvako iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple reflects:"

msgctxt "an8.45:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘yāvajīvaṃ arahanto pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā nihitadaṇḍā "
"nihitasatthā lajjī dayāpannā sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampino viharanti."
msgstr ""
"‘As long as they live the perfected ones give up killing living creatures, "
"renouncing the rod and the sword. They are scrupulous and kind, and live "
"full of compassion for all living beings."

msgctxt "an8.45:2.5"
msgid ""
"Ahampajja imañca rattiṃ imañca divasaṃ pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā "
"paṭivirato nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho lajjī dayāpanno, "
"sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"I, too, for this day and night will give up killing living creatures, "
"renouncing the rod and the sword. I’ll be scrupulous and kind, and live full "
"of compassion for all living beings."

msgctxt "an8.45:2.6"
msgid ""
"Imināpaṅgena arahataṃ anukaromi, uposatho ca me upavuttho bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"I will observe the sabbath by doing as the perfected ones do in this "
"respect.’"

msgctxt "an8.45:2.7"
msgid "Iminā paṭhamena aṅgena samannāgato hoti … pe …."
msgstr "This is its first factor. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:3.1"
msgid ""
"‘Yāvajīvaṃ arahanto uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ pahāya uccāsayanamahāsayanā "
"paṭiviratā nīcaseyyaṃ kappenti—mañcake vā tiṇasanthārake vā."
msgstr ""
"‘As long as they live the perfected ones give up high and luxurious beds. "
"They sleep in a low place, either a small bed or a straw mat."

msgctxt "an8.45:3.2"
msgid ""
"Ahampajja imañca rattiṃ imañca divasaṃ uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ pahāya "
"uccāsayanamahāsayanā paṭivirato nīcaseyyaṃ kappemi—mañcake vā tiṇasanthārake "
"vā."
msgstr ""
"I, too, for this day and night will give up high and luxurious beds. I’ll "
"sleep in a low place, either a small bed or a straw mat."

msgctxt "an8.45:3.3"
msgid ""
"Imināpaṅgena arahataṃ anukaromi, uposatho ca me upavuttho bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"I will observe the sabbath by doing as the perfected ones do in this "
"respect.’"

msgctxt "an8.45:3.4"
msgid "Iminā aṭṭhamena aṅgena samannāgato hoti."
msgstr "This is its eighth factor."

msgctxt "an8.45:3.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ upavuttho kho, bojjhe, aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgato uposatho mahapphalo hoti "
"mahānisaṃso mahājutiko mahāvipphāro."
msgstr ""
"The observance of the sabbath with its eight factors in this way is very "
"fruitful and beneficial and splendid and bountiful."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.261"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:4.1"
msgid "Kīvamahapphalo hoti, kīvamahānisaṃso, kīvamahājutiko, kīvamahāvipphāro?"
msgstr "How much so?"

msgctxt "an8.45:4.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bojjhe, yo imesaṃ soḷasannaṃ mahājanapadānaṃ "
"pahūtarattaratanānaṃ issariyādhipaccaṃ rajjaṃ kāreyya, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Suppose you were to rule as sovereign lord over these sixteen great "
"countries—Aṅga, Magadha, Kāsī, Kosala, Vajjī, Malla, Ceti, Vaṅga, Kuru, "
"Pañcāla, Maccha, Sūrusena, Assaka, Avanti, Gandhāra, and Kamboja—full of the "
"seven kinds of precious things."

msgctxt "an8.45:4.3"
msgid ""
"aṅgānaṃ magadhānaṃ kāsīnaṃ kosalānaṃ vajjīnaṃ mallānaṃ cetīnaṃ vaṅgānaṃ "
"kurūnaṃ pañcālānaṃ macchānaṃ sūrasenānaṃ assakānaṃ avantīnaṃ gandhārānaṃ "
"kambojānaṃ, aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgatassa uposathassa etaṃ kalaṃ nāgghati soḷasiṃ."
msgstr ""
"This wouldn’t be worth a sixteenth part of the sabbath with its eight "
"factors."

msgctxt "an8.45:4.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an8.45:4.5"
msgid "Kapaṇaṃ, bojjhe, mānusakaṃ rajjaṃ dibbaṃ sukhaṃ upanidhāya."
msgstr ""
"Because human kingship is a poor thing compared to the happiness of the gods."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yāni, bojjhe, mānusakāni paññāsa vassāni, cātumahārājikānaṃ devānaṃ eso eko "
"rattindivo."
msgstr ""
"Fifty years in the human realm is one day and night for the Gods of the Four "
"Great Kings."

msgctxt "an8.45:5.2"
msgid "Tāya rattiyā tiṃsarattiyo māso."
msgstr "Thirty such days make up a month."

msgctxt "an8.45:5.3"
msgid "Tena māsena dvādasamāsiyo saṃvaccharo."
msgstr "Twelve such months make up a year."

msgctxt "an8.45:5.4"
msgid ""
"Tena saṃvaccharena dibbāni pañca vassasatāni cātumahārājikānaṃ devānaṃ "
"āyuppamāṇaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The life span of the Gods of the Four Great Kings is five hundred of these "
"divine years."

msgctxt "an8.45:5.5"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, bojjhe, vijjati yaṃ idhekacco itthī vā puriso vā "
"aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgataṃ uposathaṃ upavasitvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā "
"cātumahārājikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyya."
msgstr ""
"It’s possible that a woman or man who has observed the eight-factored "
"sabbath will—when their body breaks up, after death—be reborn in the company "
"of the Gods of the Four Great Kings."

msgctxt "an8.45:5.6"
msgid "Idaṃ kho panetaṃ, bojjhe, sandhāya bhāsitaṃ:"
msgstr "This is what I was referring to when I said:"

msgctxt "an8.45:5.7"
msgid "‘kapaṇaṃ mānusakaṃ rajjaṃ dibbaṃ sukhaṃ upanidhāya’."
msgstr "‘Human kingship is a poor thing compared to the happiness of the gods.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:6.1"
msgid "Yaṃ, bojjhe, mānusakaṃ vassasataṃ … pe …"
msgstr "A hundred years in the human realm …"

msgctxt "an8.45:6.2"
msgid "tāni, bojjhe, mānusakāni dve vassasatāni … pe …"
msgstr "Two hundred years in the human realm …"

msgctxt "an8.45:6.3"
msgid "cattāri vassasatāni … pe …"
msgstr "Four hundred years in the human realm …"

msgctxt "an8.45:6.4"
msgid "aṭṭha vassasatāni … pe …"
msgstr "Eight hundred years in the human realm …"

msgctxt "an8.45:6.5"
msgid "soḷasa vassasatāni paranimmitavasavattīnaṃ devānaṃ eso eko rattindivo."
msgstr ""
"Sixteen hundred years in the human realm is one day and night for the Gods "
"Who Control the Creations of Others."

msgctxt "an8.45:6.6"
msgid "Tāya rattiyā tiṃsarattiyo māso."
msgstr "Thirty such days make up a month."

msgctxt "an8.45:6.7"
msgid "Tena māsena dvādasamāsiyo saṃvaccharo."
msgstr "Twelve such months make up a year."

msgctxt "an8.45:6.8"
msgid ""
"Tena saṃvaccharena dibbāni soḷasa vassasahassāni paranimmitavasavattīnaṃ "
"devānaṃ āyuppamāṇaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The life span of the gods who control the creations of others is sixteen "
"thousand of these divine years."

msgctxt "an8.45:6.9"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, bojjhe, vijjati yaṃ idhekacco itthī vā puriso vā "
"aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgataṃ uposathaṃ upavasitvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā "
"paranimmitavasavattīnaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyya."
msgstr ""
"It’s possible that a woman or man who has observed the eight-factored "
"sabbath will—when their body breaks up, after death—be reborn in the company "
"of the Gods Who Control the Creations of Others."

msgctxt "an8.45:6.10"
msgid "Idaṃ kho panetaṃ, bojjhe, sandhāya bhāsitaṃ:"
msgstr "This is what I was referring to when I said:"

msgctxt "an8.45:6.11"
msgid "‘kapaṇaṃ mānusakaṃ rajjaṃ dibbaṃ sukhaṃ upanidhāyā’ti."
msgstr "‘Human kingship is a poor thing compared to the happiness of the gods.’"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.262"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:7.1"
msgid "Pāṇaṃ na haññe na cadinnamādiye,"
msgstr "You shouldn’t kill living creatures, or steal,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:7.2"
msgid "Musā na bhāse na ca majjapo siyā;"
msgstr "or lie, or drink alcohol."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:7.3"
msgid "Abrahmacariyā virameyya methunā,"
msgstr "Be celibate, refraining from sex,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:7.4"
msgid "Rattiṃ na bhuñjeyya vikālabhojanaṃ."
msgstr "and don’t eat at night, the wrong time."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:8.1"
msgid "Mālaṃ na dhāre na ca gandhamācare,"
msgstr "Not wearing garlands or applying perfumes,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:8.2"
msgid "Mañce chamāyaṃ va sayetha santhate;"
msgstr "you should sleep on a low bed, or a mat on the ground."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:8.3"
msgid "Etañhi aṭṭhaṅgikamāhuposathaṃ,"
msgstr "This is the eight-factored sabbath, they say,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:8.4"
msgid "Buddhena dukkhantagunā pakāsitaṃ."
msgstr "explained by the Buddha, who has gone to suffering’s end."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:9.1"
msgid "Cando ca suriyo ca ubho sudassanā,"
msgstr "The moon and sun are both fair to see,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:9.2"
msgid "Obhāsayaṃ anupariyanti yāvatā;"
msgstr "radiating as far as they revolve."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:9.3"
msgid "Tamonudā te pana antalikkhagā,"
msgstr "Those shining ones in the sky light up the quarters,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:9.4"
msgid "Nabhe pabhāsanti disāvirocanā."
msgstr "dispelling the darkness as they traverse the heavens."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:10.1"
msgid "Etasmiṃ yaṃ vijjati antare dhanaṃ,"
msgstr "All of the wealth that’s found in this realm—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:10.2"
msgid "Muttā maṇi veḷuriyañca bhaddakaṃ;"
msgstr "pearls, gems, fine beryl too,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:10.3"
msgid "Siṅgīsuvaṇṇaṃ atha vāpi kañcanaṃ,"
msgstr "horn-gold or mountain gold,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:10.4"
msgid "Yaṃ jātarūpaṃ haṭakanti vuccati."
msgstr "or natural gold dug up by marmots—"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:11.1"
msgid "Aṭṭhaṅgupetassa uposathassa,"
msgstr "they’re not worth a sixteenth part"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:11.2"
msgid "Kalampi te nānubhavanti soḷasiṃ;"
msgstr "of the mind developed with love,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:11.3"
msgid "Candappabhā tāragaṇā ca sabbe."
msgstr "as all the constellations of stars can’t equal the light of the moon."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an8.45:12.1"
msgid "Tasmā hi nārī ca naro ca sīlavā,"
msgstr "So an ethical woman or man,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:12.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhaṅgupetaṃ upavassuposathaṃ;"
msgstr "who has observed the eight-factored sabbath,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:12.3"
msgid "Puññāni katvāna sukhudrayāni,"
msgstr "having made merit whose outcome is happiness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.45:12.4"
msgid "Aninditā saggamupenti ṭhānan”ti."
msgstr "blameless, they go to a heavenly place.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.45:12.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
